name: Jason Carrington
summary:
Jason Carrington is a 32-year old straight man from San Francisco, California, who is currently living in Los Angeles. He is a successful software engineer in the technology industry and a Stanford University graduate. Fluent in English and Spanish, Jason values compassion, honesty, and ambition. He enjoys traveling, cooking, and reading in his spare time. 

On a personal level, he identifies as Agnostic and politically moderate. Although he doesn't have any children, he hopes to become a father in the future. Jason is a cat owner who hardly drinks and doesn't smoke or use any sort of drugs. 

As an active, health-conscious individual, he is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship with a straight woman aged between 26 and 35 who shares similar lifestyle habits and values. This includes a preference for someone who doesn't smoke, has no children but wants them in the future, and enjoys an active lifestyle.
